&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>30. 串联所有单词的子串</title><link>https://kerolt.github.io/p/30.-%E4%B8%B2%E8%81%94%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%B2/</link><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kerolt.github.io/p/30.-%E4%B8%B2%E8%81%94%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%95%E8%AF%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%B2/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;难度：Hard&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;标签：哈希表、字符串、滑动窗口&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;链接：https://leetcode.cn/problems/substring-with-concatenation-of-all-words/description/&lt;/p&gt;

 &lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在B站上看见一个up的视频，感觉说的很清晰，言简意赅：&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Tg4y1z7jR/?share_source=copy_web&amp;amp;vd_source=158b66457253e14c958ac7e040b420c9" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
